32static const char kDefaultVideoSenderId[] = "defaultv0";

36RtpTransmissionManager::RtpTransmissionManager(
37 bool is_unified_plan,
38 rtc::Thread* signaling_thread,
39 rtc::Thread* worker_thread,
40 cricket::ChannelManager* channel_manager,
41 UsagePattern* usage_pattern,
42 PeerConnectionObserver* observer,
43 StatsCollectorInterface* stats,
44 std::function<void()> on_negotiation_needed)
45 : is_unified_plan_(is_unified_plan),
46 signaling_thread_(signaling_thread),
47 worker_thread_(worker_thread),
48 channel_manager_(channel_manager),
49 usage_pattern_(usage_pattern),
50 observer_(observer),
51 stats_(stats),
52 on_negotiation_needed_(on_negotiation_needed),
53 weak_ptr_factory_(this) {}
54
55void RtpTransmissionManager::Close() {
56 closed_ = true;
57 observer_ = nullptr;
58}
59
60// Implementation of SetStreamsObserver
61void RtpTransmissionManager::OnSetStreams() {
62 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
63 if (IsUnifiedPlan())
64 OnNegotiationNeeded();
65}
66
67// Function to call back to the PeerConnection when negotiation is needed
68void RtpTransmissionManager::OnNegotiationNeeded() {
69 on_negotiation_needed_();
70}
71
72// Function that returns the currently valid observer
73PeerConnectionObserver* RtpTransmissionManager::Observer() const {
74 RTC_DCHECK(!closed_);
75 RTC_DCHECK(observer_);
76 return observer_;
77}

79cricket::VoiceMediaChannel* RtpTransmissionManager::voice_media_channel()
80 const {
81 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
82 RTC_DCHECK(!IsUnifiedPlan());
83 auto* voice_channel = static_cast<cricket::VoiceChannel*>(
84 GetAudioTransceiver()->internal()->channel());
85 if (voice_channel) {
86 return voice_channel->media_channel();
87 } else {
88 return nullptr;
89 }
90}

92cricket::VideoMediaChannel* RtpTransmissionManager::video_media_channel()
93 const {
94 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
95 RTC_DCHECK(!IsUnifiedPlan());
96 auto* video_channel = static_cast<cricket::VideoChannel*>(
97 GetVideoTransceiver()->internal()->channel());
98 if (video_channel) {
99 return video_channel->media_channel();
100 } else {
101 return nullptr;
102 }

105RTCErrorOr<rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpSenderInterface>>
106RtpTransmissionManager::AddTrack(
107 rtc::scoped_refptr<MediaStreamTrackInterface> track,
108 const std::vector<std::string>& stream_ids) {
109 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
110
111 return (IsUnifiedPlan() ? AddTrackUnifiedPlan(track, stream_ids)
112 : AddTrackPlanB(track, stream_ids));
113}
114
115RTCErrorOr<rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpSenderInterface>>
116RtpTransmissionManager::AddTrackPlanB(
117 rtc::scoped_refptr<MediaStreamTrackInterface> track,
118 const std::vector<std::string>& stream_ids) {
119 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
120 if (stream_ids.size() > 1u) {
121 LOG_AND_RETURN_ERROR(RTCErrorType::UNSUPPORTED_OPERATION,
122 "AddTrack with more than one stream is not "
123 "supported with Plan B semantics.");
124 }
125 std::vector<std::string> adjusted_stream_ids = stream_ids;
126 if (adjusted_stream_ids.empty()) {
127 adjusted_stream_ids.push_back(rtc::CreateRandomUuid());
128 }
129 cricket::MediaType media_type =
130 (track->kind() == MediaStreamTrackInterface::kAudioKind
131 ? cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_AUDIO
132 : cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_VIDEO);
133 auto new_sender =
134 CreateSender(media_type, track->id(), track, adjusted_stream_ids, {});
135 if (track->kind() == MediaStreamTrackInterface::kAudioKind) {
136 new_sender->internal()->SetMediaChannel(voice_media_channel());
137 GetAudioTransceiver()->internal()->AddSender(new_sender);
138 const RtpSenderInfo* sender_info =
139 FindSenderInfo(local_audio_sender_infos_,
140 new_sender->internal()->stream_ids()[0], track->id());
141 if (sender_info) {
142 new_sender->internal()->SetSsrc(sender_info->first_ssrc);
143 }
144 } else {
145 RTC_DCHECK_EQ(MediaStreamTrackInterface::kVideoKind, track->kind());
146 new_sender->internal()->SetMediaChannel(video_media_channel());
147 GetVideoTransceiver()->internal()->AddSender(new_sender);
148 const RtpSenderInfo* sender_info =
149 FindSenderInfo(local_video_sender_infos_,
150 new_sender->internal()->stream_ids()[0], track->id());
151 if (sender_info) {
152 new_sender->internal()->SetSsrc(sender_info->first_ssrc);
153 }
154 }
155 return rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpSenderInterface>(new_sender);
156}
157
158RTCErrorOr<rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpSenderInterface>>
159RtpTransmissionManager::AddTrackUnifiedPlan(
160 rtc::scoped_refptr<MediaStreamTrackInterface> track,
161 const std::vector<std::string>& stream_ids) {
162 auto transceiver = FindFirstTransceiverForAddedTrack(track);
163 if (transceiver) {
164 RTC_LOG(LS_INFO) << "Reusing an existing "
165 << cricket::MediaTypeToString(transceiver->media_type())
166 << " transceiver for AddTrack.";
167 if (transceiver->stopping()) {
168 LOG_AND_RETURN_ERROR(RTCErrorType::INVALID_PARAMETER,
169 "The existing transceiver is stopping.");
170 }
171
172 if (transceiver->direction() == RtpTransceiverDirection::kRecvOnly) {
173 transceiver->internal()->set_direction(
174 RtpTransceiverDirection::kSendRecv);
175 } else if (transceiver->direction() == RtpTransceiverDirection::kInactive) {
176 transceiver->internal()->set_direction(
177 RtpTransceiverDirection::kSendOnly);
178 }
179 transceiver->sender()->SetTrack(track);
180 transceiver->internal()->sender_internal()->set_stream_ids(stream_ids);
181 transceiver->internal()->set_reused_for_addtrack(true);
182 } else {
183 cricket::MediaType media_type =
184 (track->kind() == MediaStreamTrackInterface::kAudioKind
185 ? cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_AUDIO
186 : cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_VIDEO);
187 RTC_LOG(LS_INFO) << "Adding " << cricket::MediaTypeToString(media_type)
188 << " transceiver in response to a call to AddTrack.";
189 std::string sender_id = track->id();
190 // Avoid creating a sender with an existing ID by generating a random ID.
191 // This can happen if this is the second time AddTrack has created a sender
192 // for this track.
193 if (FindSenderById(sender_id)) {
194 sender_id = rtc::CreateRandomUuid();
195 }
196 auto sender = CreateSender(media_type, sender_id, track, stream_ids, {});
197 auto receiver = CreateReceiver(media_type, rtc::CreateRandomUuid());
198 transceiver = CreateAndAddTransceiver(sender, receiver);
199 transceiver->internal()->set_created_by_addtrack(true);
200 transceiver->internal()->set_direction(RtpTransceiverDirection::kSendRecv);
201 }
202 return transceiver->sender();
203}

205rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpSenderProxyWithInternal<RtpSenderInternal>>
206RtpTransmissionManager::CreateSender(
207 cricket::MediaType media_type,
208 const std::string& id,
209 rtc::scoped_refptr<MediaStreamTrackInterface> track,
210 const std::vector<std::string>& stream_ids,
211 const std::vector<RtpEncodingParameters>& send_encodings) {
212 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
213 rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpSenderProxyWithInternal<RtpSenderInternal>> sender;
214 if (media_type == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_AUDIO) {
215 RTC_DCHECK(!track ||
216 (track->kind() == MediaStreamTrackInterface::kAudioKind));
217 sender = RtpSenderProxyWithInternal<RtpSenderInternal>::Create(
218 signaling_thread(),
219 AudioRtpSender::Create(worker_thread(), id, stats_, this));
220 NoteUsageEvent(UsageEvent::AUDIO_ADDED);
221 } else {
222 RTC_DCHECK_EQ(media_type, cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_VIDEO);
223 RTC_DCHECK(!track ||
224 (track->kind() == MediaStreamTrackInterface::kVideoKind));
225 sender = RtpSenderProxyWithInternal<RtpSenderInternal>::Create(
226 signaling_thread(), VideoRtpSender::Create(worker_thread(), id, this));
227 NoteUsageEvent(UsageEvent::VIDEO_ADDED);
228 }
229 bool set_track_succeeded = sender->SetTrack(track);
230 RTC_DCHECK(set_track_succeeded);
231 sender->internal()->set_stream_ids(stream_ids);
232 sender->internal()->set_init_send_encodings(send_encodings);
233 return sender;
234}
235
236rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpReceiverProxyWithInternal<RtpReceiverInternal>>
237RtpTransmissionManager::CreateReceiver(cricket::MediaType media_type,
238 const std::string& receiver_id) {
239 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
240 rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpReceiverProxyWithInternal<RtpReceiverInternal>>
241 receiver;
242 if (media_type == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_AUDIO) {
243 receiver = RtpReceiverProxyWithInternal<RtpReceiverInternal>::Create(
244 signaling_thread(), worker_thread(),
245 rtc::make_ref_counted<AudioRtpReceiver>(worker_thread(), receiver_id,
246 std::vector<std::string>({}),
247 IsUnifiedPlan()));
248 NoteUsageEvent(UsageEvent::AUDIO_ADDED);
249 } else {
250 RTC_DCHECK_EQ(media_type, cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_VIDEO);
251 receiver = RtpReceiverProxyWithInternal<RtpReceiverInternal>::Create(
252 signaling_thread(), worker_thread(),
253 rtc::make_ref_counted<VideoRtpReceiver>(worker_thread(), receiver_id,
254 std::vector<std::string>({})));
255 NoteUsageEvent(UsageEvent::VIDEO_ADDED);
256 }
257 return receiver;
258}
259
260rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpTransceiverProxyWithInternal<RtpTransceiver>>
261RtpTransmissionManager::CreateAndAddTransceiver(
262 rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpSenderProxyWithInternal<RtpSenderInternal>> sender,
263 rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpReceiverProxyWithInternal<RtpReceiverInternal>>
264 receiver) {
265 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
266 // Ensure that the new sender does not have an ID that is already in use by
267 // another sender.
268 // Allow receiver IDs to conflict since those come from remote SDP (which
269 // could be invalid, but should not cause a crash).
270 RTC_DCHECK(!FindSenderById(sender->id()));
271 auto transceiver = RtpTransceiverProxyWithInternal<RtpTransceiver>::Create(
272 signaling_thread(),
273 new RtpTransceiver(
274 sender, receiver, channel_manager(),
275 sender->media_type() == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_AUDIO
276 ? channel_manager()->GetSupportedAudioRtpHeaderExtensions()
277 : channel_manager()->GetSupportedVideoRtpHeaderExtensions(),
278 [this_weak_ptr = weak_ptr_factory_.GetWeakPtr()]() {
279 if (this_weak_ptr) {
280 this_weak_ptr->OnNegotiationNeeded();
281 }
282 }));
283 transceivers()->Add(transceiver);
284 return transceiver;
285}
286
287rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpTransceiverProxyWithInternal<RtpTransceiver>>
288RtpTransmissionManager::FindFirstTransceiverForAddedTrack(
289 rtc::scoped_refptr<MediaStreamTrackInterface> track) {
290 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
291 RTC_DCHECK(track);
292 for (auto transceiver : transceivers()->List()) {
293 if (!transceiver->sender()->track() &&
294 cricket::MediaTypeToString(transceiver->media_type()) ==
295 track->kind() &&
296 !transceiver->internal()->has_ever_been_used_to_send() &&
297 !transceiver->stopped()) {
298 return transceiver;
299 }
300 }
301 return nullptr;
302}
303
304std::vector<rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpSenderProxyWithInternal<RtpSenderInternal>>>
305RtpTransmissionManager::GetSendersInternal() const {
306 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
307 std::vector<rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpSenderProxyWithInternal<RtpSenderInternal>>>
308 all_senders;
309 for (const auto& transceiver : transceivers_.List()) {
310 if (IsUnifiedPlan() && transceiver->internal()->stopped())
311 continue;
312
313 auto senders = transceiver->internal()->senders();
314 all_senders.insert(all_senders.end(), senders.begin(), senders.end());
315 }
316 return all_senders;
317}
318
319std::vector<
320 rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpReceiverProxyWithInternal<RtpReceiverInternal>>>
321RtpTransmissionManager::GetReceiversInternal() const {
322 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
323 std::vector<
324 rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpReceiverProxyWithInternal<RtpReceiverInternal>>>
325 all_receivers;
326 for (const auto& transceiver : transceivers_.List()) {
327 if (IsUnifiedPlan() && transceiver->internal()->stopped())
328 continue;
329
330 auto receivers = transceiver->internal()->receivers();
331 all_receivers.insert(all_receivers.end(), receivers.begin(),
332 receivers.end());
333 }
334 return all_receivers;
335}

337rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpTransceiverProxyWithInternal<RtpTransceiver>>
338RtpTransmissionManager::GetAudioTransceiver() const {
339 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
340 // This method only works with Plan B SDP, where there is a single
341 // audio/video transceiver.
342 RTC_DCHECK(!IsUnifiedPlan());
343 for (auto transceiver : transceivers_.List()) {
344 if (transceiver->media_type() == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_AUDIO) {
345 return transceiver;
346 }
347 }
348 RTC_NOTREACHED();
349 return nullptr;
350}

352rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpTransceiverProxyWithInternal<RtpTransceiver>>
353RtpTransmissionManager::GetVideoTransceiver() const {
354 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
355 // This method only works with Plan B SDP, where there is a single
356 // audio/video transceiver.
357 RTC_DCHECK(!IsUnifiedPlan());
358 for (auto transceiver : transceivers_.List()) {
359 if (transceiver->media_type() == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_VIDEO) {
360 return transceiver;
361 }
362 }
363 RTC_NOTREACHED();
364 return nullptr;
365}

367void RtpTransmissionManager::AddAudioTrack(AudioTrackInterface* track,
368 MediaStreamInterface* stream) {
369 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
370 RTC_DCHECK(track);
371 RTC_DCHECK(stream);
372 auto sender = FindSenderForTrack(track);
373 if (sender) {
374 // We already have a sender for this track, so just change the stream_id
375 // so that it's correct in the next call to CreateOffer.
376 sender->internal()->set_stream_ids({stream->id()});
377 return;
378 }
379
380 // Normal case; we've never seen this track before.
381 auto new_sender = CreateSender(cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_AUDIO, track->id(), track,
382 {stream->id()}, {});
383 new_sender->internal()->SetMediaChannel(voice_media_channel());
384 GetAudioTransceiver()->internal()->AddSender(new_sender);
385 // If the sender has already been configured in SDP, we call SetSsrc,
386 // which will connect the sender to the underlying transport. This can
387 // occur if a local session description that contains the ID of the sender
388 // is set before AddStream is called. It can also occur if the local
389 // session description is not changed and RemoveStream is called, and
390 // later AddStream is called again with the same stream.
391 const RtpSenderInfo* sender_info =
392 FindSenderInfo(local_audio_sender_infos_, stream->id(), track->id());
393 if (sender_info) {
394 new_sender->internal()->SetSsrc(sender_info->first_ssrc);
395 }
396}
397
398// TODO(deadbeef): Don't destroy RtpSenders here; they should be kept around
399// indefinitely, when we have unified plan SDP.
400void RtpTransmissionManager::RemoveAudioTrack(AudioTrackInterface* track,
401 MediaStreamInterface* stream) {
402 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
403 RTC_DCHECK(!IsUnifiedPlan());
404 auto sender = FindSenderForTrack(track);
405 if (!sender) {
406 RTC_LOG(LS_WARNING) << "RtpSender for track with id " << track->id()
407 << " doesn't exist.";
408 return;
409 }
410 GetAudioTransceiver()->internal()->RemoveSender(sender);
411}

451void RtpTransmissionManager::CreateAudioReceiver(
452 MediaStreamInterface* stream,
453 const RtpSenderInfo& remote_sender_info) {
454 RTC_DCHECK(!closed_);
455 std::vector<rtc::scoped_refptr<MediaStreamInterface>> streams;
456 streams.push_back(rtc::scoped_refptr<MediaStreamInterface>(stream));
457 // TODO(https://crbug.com/webrtc/9480): When we remove remote_streams(), use
458 // the constructor taking stream IDs instead.
459 auto audio_receiver = rtc::make_ref_counted<AudioRtpReceiver>(
460 worker_thread(), remote_sender_info.sender_id, streams, IsUnifiedPlan());
461 audio_receiver->SetMediaChannel(voice_media_channel());
462 if (remote_sender_info.sender_id == kDefaultAudioSenderId) {
463 audio_receiver->SetupUnsignaledMediaChannel();
464 } else {
465 audio_receiver->SetupMediaChannel(remote_sender_info.first_ssrc);
466 }
467 auto receiver = RtpReceiverProxyWithInternal<RtpReceiverInternal>::Create(
468 signaling_thread(), worker_thread(), std::move(audio_receiver));
469 GetAudioTransceiver()->internal()->AddReceiver(receiver);
470 Observer()->OnAddTrack(receiver, streams);
471 NoteUsageEvent(UsageEvent::AUDIO_ADDED);
472}
473
474void RtpTransmissionManager::CreateVideoReceiver(
475 MediaStreamInterface* stream,
476 const RtpSenderInfo& remote_sender_info) {
477 RTC_DCHECK(!closed_);
478 std::vector<rtc::scoped_refptr<MediaStreamInterface>> streams;
479 streams.push_back(rtc::scoped_refptr<MediaStreamInterface>(stream));
480 // TODO(https://crbug.com/webrtc/9480): When we remove remote_streams(), use
481 // the constructor taking stream IDs instead.
482 auto video_receiver = rtc::make_ref_counted<VideoRtpReceiver>(
483 worker_thread(), remote_sender_info.sender_id, streams);
484 video_receiver->SetMediaChannel(video_media_channel());
485 if (remote_sender_info.sender_id == kDefaultVideoSenderId) {
486 video_receiver->SetupUnsignaledMediaChannel();
487 } else {
488 video_receiver->SetupMediaChannel(remote_sender_info.first_ssrc);
489 }
490 auto receiver = RtpReceiverProxyWithInternal<RtpReceiverInternal>::Create(
491 signaling_thread(), worker_thread(), std::move(video_receiver));
492 GetVideoTransceiver()->internal()->AddReceiver(receiver);
493 Observer()->OnAddTrack(receiver, streams);
494 NoteUsageEvent(UsageEvent::VIDEO_ADDED);
495}

497// TODO(deadbeef): Keep RtpReceivers around even if track goes away in remote
498// description.
499rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpReceiverInterface>
500RtpTransmissionManager::RemoveAndStopReceiver(
501 const RtpSenderInfo& remote_sender_info) {
502 auto receiver = FindReceiverById(remote_sender_info.sender_id);
503 if (!receiver) {
504 RTC_LOG(LS_WARNING) << "RtpReceiver for track with id "
505 << remote_sender_info.sender_id << " doesn't exist.";
506 return nullptr;
507 }
508 if (receiver->media_type() == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_AUDIO) {
509 GetAudioTransceiver()->internal()->RemoveReceiver(receiver);
510 } else {
511 GetVideoTransceiver()->internal()->RemoveReceiver(receiver);
512 }
513 return receiver;
514}
515
516void RtpTransmissionManager::OnRemoteSenderAdded(
517 const RtpSenderInfo& sender_info,
518 MediaStreamInterface* stream,
519 cricket::MediaType media_type) {
520 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
521 RTC_LOG(LS_INFO) << "Creating " << cricket::MediaTypeToString(media_type)
522 << " receiver for track_id=" << sender_info.sender_id
523 << " and stream_id=" << sender_info.stream_id;
524
525 if (media_type == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_AUDIO) {
526 CreateAudioReceiver(stream, sender_info);
527 } else if (media_type == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_VIDEO) {
528 CreateVideoReceiver(stream, sender_info);
529 } else {
530 RTC_NOTREACHED() << "Invalid media type";
531 }
532}
533
534void RtpTransmissionManager::OnRemoteSenderRemoved(
535 const RtpSenderInfo& sender_info,
536 MediaStreamInterface* stream,
537 cricket::MediaType media_type) {
538 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
539 RTC_LOG(LS_INFO) << "Removing " << cricket::MediaTypeToString(media_type)
540 << " receiver for track_id=" << sender_info.sender_id
541 << " and stream_id=" << sender_info.stream_id;
542
543 rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpReceiverInterface> receiver;
544 if (media_type == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_AUDIO) {
545 // When the MediaEngine audio channel is destroyed, the RemoteAudioSource
546 // will be notified which will end the AudioRtpReceiver::track().
547 receiver = RemoveAndStopReceiver(sender_info);
548 rtc::scoped_refptr<AudioTrackInterface> audio_track =
549 stream->FindAudioTrack(sender_info.sender_id);
550 if (audio_track) {
551 stream->RemoveTrack(audio_track);
552 }
553 } else if (media_type == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_VIDEO) {
554 // Stopping or destroying a VideoRtpReceiver will end the
555 // VideoRtpReceiver::track().
556 receiver = RemoveAndStopReceiver(sender_info);
557 rtc::scoped_refptr<VideoTrackInterface> video_track =
558 stream->FindVideoTrack(sender_info.sender_id);
559 if (video_track) {
560 // There's no guarantee the track is still available, e.g. the track may
561 // have been removed from the stream by an application.
562 stream->RemoveTrack(video_track);
563 }
564 } else {
565 RTC_NOTREACHED() << "Invalid media type";
566 }
567 if (receiver) {
568 RTC_DCHECK(!closed_);
569 Observer()->OnRemoveTrack(receiver);
570 }
571}
572
573void RtpTransmissionManager::OnLocalSenderAdded(
574 const RtpSenderInfo& sender_info,
575 cricket::MediaType media_type) {
576 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
577 RTC_DCHECK(!IsUnifiedPlan());
578 auto sender = FindSenderById(sender_info.sender_id);
579 if (!sender) {
580 RTC_LOG(LS_WARNING) << "An unknown RtpSender with id "
581 << sender_info.sender_id
582 << " has been configured in the local description.";
583 return;
584 }
585
586 if (sender->media_type() != media_type) {
587 RTC_LOG(LS_WARNING) << "An RtpSender has been configured in the local"
588 " description with an unexpected media type.";
589 return;
590 }
591
592 sender->internal()->set_stream_ids({sender_info.stream_id});
593 sender->internal()->SetSsrc(sender_info.first_ssrc);
594}
595
596void RtpTransmissionManager::OnLocalSenderRemoved(
597 const RtpSenderInfo& sender_info,
598 cricket::MediaType media_type) {
599 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
600 auto sender = FindSenderById(sender_info.sender_id);
601 if (!sender) {
602 // This is the normal case. I.e., RemoveStream has been called and the
603 // SessionDescriptions has been renegotiated.
604 return;
605 }
606
607 // A sender has been removed from the SessionDescription but it's still
608 // associated with the PeerConnection. This only occurs if the SDP doesn't
609 // match with the calls to CreateSender, AddStream and RemoveStream.
610 if (sender->media_type() != media_type) {
611 RTC_LOG(LS_WARNING) << "An RtpSender has been configured in the local"
612 " description with an unexpected media type.";
613 return;
614 }
615
616 sender->internal()->SetSsrc(0);
617}
618
619std::vector<RtpSenderInfo>* RtpTransmissionManager::GetRemoteSenderInfos(
620 cricket::MediaType media_type) {
621 RTC_DCHECK(media_type == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_AUDIO ||
622 media_type == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_VIDEO);
623 return (media_type == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_AUDIO)
624 ? &remote_audio_sender_infos_
625 : &remote_video_sender_infos_;
626}

628std::vector<RtpSenderInfo>* RtpTransmissionManager::GetLocalSenderInfos(
629 cricket::MediaType media_type) {
630 RTC_DCHECK(media_type == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_AUDIO ||
631 media_type == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_VIDEO);
632 return (media_type == cricket::MEDIA_TYPE_AUDIO) ? &local_audio_sender_infos_
633 : &local_video_sender_infos_;
634}

636const RtpSenderInfo* RtpTransmissionManager::FindSenderInfo(
637 const std::vector<RtpSenderInfo>& infos,
638 const std::string& stream_id,
639 const std::string sender_id) const {
640 for (const RtpSenderInfo& sender_info : infos) {
641 if (sender_info.stream_id == stream_id &&
642 sender_info.sender_id == sender_id) {
643 return &sender_info;
644 }
645 }
646 return nullptr;
647}

649rtc::scoped_refptr<RtpSenderProxyWithInternal<RtpSenderInternal>>
650RtpTransmissionManager::FindSenderForTrack(
651 MediaStreamTrackInterface* track) const {
652 RTC_DCHECK_RUN_ON(signaling_thread());
653 for (const auto& transceiver : transceivers_.List()) {
654 for (auto sender : transceiver->internal()->senders()) {
655 if (sender->track() == track) {
656 return sender;
657 }
658 }
659 }
660 return nullptr;
661}
